Global Pet Hemostatic Forceps Market Insights
Pet Hemostatic Forceps Market size was valued at USD 0.45 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.85 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Pet Hemostatic Forceps Market Overview
The Pet Hemostatic Forceps market is a key component of the global veterinary surgical instrument sector. In 2024, the market value of pet hemostatic forceps is estimated to reach USD 150 million, with a projected compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.6% from 2025 to 2030. This growth is attributed to increasing pet ownership, the rise in veterinary surgeries, and advancements in medical equipment for pets. The demand for pet care services, especially surgical interventions, is rising, influencing the adoption of precise and reliable tools such as hemostatic forceps for controlling bleeding during surgeries.

